---
import {
  DEVICE_COST_SESSION_KEY,
  PRESET_DEVICE_TYPES
} from "../lib/device-cost-tool";
import deviceCostToolScript from "../scripts/device-cost-tool.ts?url";
---

<section
  class="device-tool"
  data-device-cost-tool
  data-storage-key={DEVICE_COST_SESSION_KEY}
  data-preset-types={JSON.stringify(PRESET_DEVICE_TYPES.map(String))}
>
  <section class="device-tool__intro panel">
    <div class="device-tool__hero-copy">
      <h2>电子产品均价</h2>
      <p>
        录入一台正在使用的电子设备，快速算出它现在平均每天花了多少钱。换设备之前，先把这笔账看得更直观一点。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="device-tool__toolbar">
    <button type="button" class="primary-button" data-action="add-card">+ 创建卡片</button>
  </div>

  <div class="device-tool__cards" data-cards></div>
</section>

<script type="module" src={deviceCostToolScript}></script>
